The fork state changes the feasible path materially: `balanceOf(TARGET)` at the logged block is already far above the 5,000 MCC auto-swap threshold, so any non-pair transfer would trigger the sell branch before a fresh self-transfer loop can execute. I’m checking the rest of the public token surface for a realistic seed/profit route that still uses the same root cause rather than fabricating balances.
